Definition: Eurasian herb naturalized in America having white flowers and poisonous hairy foliage and bearing black berries that are sometimes poisonous but sometimes edible
Synonyms: common_nightshade, poisonberry, poison-berry, Solanum_nigrum, nightshade, Eurasian, herb, naturalized, in, America, having, white, flowers, and, poisonous, hairy, foliage, bearing, black, berries, that, are, sometimes, but, edible
Category: noun.plant
